<p>Thanks man. This is great stuff. I&#8217;ve been looking for the optimal aggregator for a while now going through raggle (good but unmaintained and shaky), centericq (just shaky), straw (GUI only) and 20 or so more.</p>

<p>A &#8216;delay&#8217; feature would be nice though.. I was stupid enough to add all my old feeds at once and hit &#8216;r2e run&#8217; without thinking&#8230; I&#8217;ve never seen procmail and bogofilter work so hard before (grin).</p>

<p>Keep up the good work! //Anders </p>

